{"tid":401190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議大學生立即懸掛支持社會主義制度標語","createTime":"2017-09-15T11:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T16:24:00.000Z","uid":19654,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74857d4fa1f1264b88f5a86026fad65d7114c019","tid":401190,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"基本法笫一條<br />\n<br />\n香港特別行政區是中華人民共和國不可分離的部分。 <br />\n<br />\n基本法第五條 <br />\n<br />\n香港特別行政區不實行社會主義制度和政策，保持原有的資本主義制度和生活方式，五十年不變。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[size=6][港獨違反基本法第一條<br />\n支持社會主義違反第五條<br />\n<br />\n你班大學校長係咪又出聲名反對先<br />\n定又玩雙重標準呀/size=6]</span>"},{"pid":"984815a4708b7f2e4f2a670f0f2be89aaeddf483","tid":401190,"uid":19654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9c002aa3a55d3c241503b3b3fa95b4deb0eb70","tid":401190,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192f81897b0e60edc90be093c7b2dfb017862327","tid":401190,"uid":1065,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:05:09.000Z","msg":"劉曉波單野已經話左比你知班撚屌有幾咁無恥幾咁雙重標準<br />\n而且你吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6030794f7cdb23728db1984bc9261b5707f2328","tid":401190,"uid":19654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劉曉波單野已經話左比你知班撚屌有幾咁無恥幾咁雙重標準<br />\n而且你吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n矛頭對準沈匪<br />\n有籍口佔領校長室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c